I think I need to go freshen this up.

19:10.180 --> 19:12.219
Just let me get that.

19:12.406 --> 19:14.039
We have a lot to catch up on.

19:19.707 --> 19:22.366
Oh my God.

19:22.763 --> 19:23.609
