wrote him into my book.

19:26.782 --> 19:28.414
- Did you?
- No.

19:28.449 --> 19:31.386
Not... not exactly.
But kind of.

19:31.796 --> 19:32.893
You remember that part

19:32.913 --> 19:37.134
where Shelly, the young wife,
has revenge sex on a train

19:37.154 --> 19:39.574
with a guy she just met?

19:43.696 --> 19:44.977
Him?

19:44.997 --> 19:46.920
Uh, well, it wasn't revenge sex...

19:46.940 --> 19:50.755
- Exactly.
- You and that guy?

19:50.775 --> 19:52.314
In the bathroom.

19:52.860 --> 19:55.247
- Of a train?
- I put paper towels down.

19:55.267 --> 19:56.309
(Sighs)

19:56.329 --> 19:59.850
- You are a wild woman.
- I only did it this one time.

19:59.870 --> 20:01.786
It was the craziest thing
I did in my whole life

20:01.806 --> 20:04.119
and I never thought I'd see the guy again.

20:04.139 --> 20:05.684
Looks like you were pretty unforgettable.

20:05.719 --> 20:07.436
I have got to ditch him.

20:07.456 --> 20:09.848
Okay, come on,
let's go talk to that Russian poet.

20:09.868 --> 20:11.226
That oughta shake him.

20:11.246 --> 20:13.119
Good idea.
(Regina laughs)

20:15.862 --> 20:18.237
(Bell rings)
(Men laughing)

20:18.708 --> 20:23.081
_

20:23.101 --> 20:26.370
It's so funny that you can hear it,
but I can't.

20:26.390 --> 20:27.812
(Phone buzzes)

20:33.086 --> 20:36.114
Uh, I have to, uh, make a call. I'll...

20:40.996 --> 20:42.751
Hey, it's you.

20:42.771 --> 20:45.245
I didn't think you were...

20:45.265 --> 20:46.481
sorry, um...

20:46.501 --> 20:48.940
Do you know who I am?

20:50.851 --> 20:52.961
I know, it's weird, right?

20:55.132 --> 20:57.967
Hi, uh, this is Bay Kennish.
I missed your call.

20:57.987 --> 21:00.006
Woman on phone: Yes, Dr. Larkin
would like you to come in tomorrow

21:00.026 --> 21:01.768
to discuss the results of your M.R.I.

21:01.788 --> 21:04.014
Um, okay.

21:04.034 --> 21:05.714
Can I talk to Dr. Larkin? Is he there?

21:05.734 --> 21:07.936
Oh, his office is closed,
but if you'd like his voicemail...

21:07.956 --> 21:09.814
No, no, um... I...

21:09.849 --> 21:11.993
I will be there at 8:40.

21:12.013 --> 21:13.627
- Okay.
- Bye-bye.

21:19.856 --> 21:21.840
Hey, look I found him.

21:21.860 --> 21:24.477
