21:24.497 --> 21:26.791
She probably just wants to
tell you how amazing you are

21:26.811 --> 21:28.814
and how she broke up with her boyfriend

21:28.834 --> 21:32.167
after she read all the things
that you wrote to Mandy

21:32.187 --> 21:35.356
because it finally showed
her what real love is.

21:35.376 --> 21:37.138
Does that help?

21:39.410 --> 21:40.638
(Sighs)

21:44.731 --> 21:46.585
