into whatever is going on with me,

22:17.081 --> 22:19.983
so you should go to L.A. or D.C.

22:20.017 --> 22:21.885
and meet new people.

22:21.919 --> 22:23.489
I... no, I just can't...

22:23.509 --> 22:26.065
no, just... Let me go.

22:35.977 --> 22:37.775
There you are.

22:38.284 --> 22:39.785
I've been carrying this Chablis around.

22:39.805 --> 22:41.168
Well, I was just, you know...

22:41.188 --> 22:43.566
