22:43.586 --> 22:46.420
- Right, guess you gotta work the room.
- Yeah.

22:46.440 --> 22:50.073
Well, when you're ready to shove off,
I was thinking we COD grab some dinner,

22:50.093 --> 22:53.678
maybe take the train
downtown for old time's sake.

22:54.088 --> 22:57.067
