23:06.978 --> 23:09.205
You look so tired, babe.

23:09.239 --> 23:11.160
Do you wanna go back to the hotel?

23:12.409 --> 23:14.429
We did book that couples massage.

23:14.449 --> 23:16.279
(Regina and Kathryn moaning)

23:16.313 --> 23:17.980
(Giggling)

23:18.147 --> 23:21.255
I guess I better tend
the home fires tonight.

23:21.275 --> 23:24.452
Wait, aren't you the other mom
from the first book?

23:24.713 --> 23:27.282
- I am.
- And you two...

23:28.200 --> 23:29.565
(Glasses clink)

23:30.194 --> 23:33.131
Oh, that's... modern.

23:33.899 --> 23:37.018
I think we both know how open-minded
Kathryn can be.

23:37.038 --> 23:39.376
So let's, um, get our coats.

23:39.396 --> 23:40.525
Okay.

23:42.201 --> 23:44.993
Definitely gave him
something to talk about.

23:46.308 --> 23:47.438
Lydia: Kathryn.

23:48.046 --> 23:49.545
Oh, um...

23:49.994 --> 23:52.527
We're just about to start the reading.

23:52.547 --> 23:54.724
I guess that massage will have to wait.

23:54.744 --> 23:57.412
- Knock 'em dead, hon.
- Thanks.

23:57.858 --> 23:59.844
Yeah, come on.

24:03.728 --> 24:05.565
