24:07.352 --> 24:08.844
You sure you don't want some?

24:08.864 --> 24:10.955
It's disgusting in the best way.

24:10.975 --> 24:12.901
Nope, I'm good.

24:12.921 --> 24:14.703
Well, I ate some crap and
I spent all my money.

24:14.737 --> 24:17.539
I think I'm done.
You want a ride home?

24:17.678 --> 24:19.433
(Straw gurgles)

24:19.453 --> 24:22.009
- No, I drove.
- I know.

24:22.029 --> 24:23.995
Maybe I should drive you home.

24:24.015 --> 24:26.638
Why is everyone such a drag?

24:26.658 --> 24:28.116
(Sighs)

24:28.904 --> 24:31.093
