24:45.167 --> 24:47.181
Come on, I'll go with you.

24:49.998 --> 24:51.181
I'll see you later.

24:51.201 --> 24:53.261
Try to have some fun.

24:56.185 --> 24:57.625
Have you seen Bay?

24:57.645 --> 24:59.970
