- Seriously, that was great.

26:07.246 --> 26:08.561
(Sighs)

26:08.581 --> 26:10.187
Not the kiss, the read.

26:10.207 --> 26:11.932
- You know what I mean.
- (Laughs) Yes.

26:12.825 --> 26:15.887
I feel like the girl who took her top off
at the dinner party.

26:15.921 --> 26:17.696
