34:07.871 --> 34:09.672
Yeah, where's Regina?

34:09.706 --> 34:11.376
Uh, I think she went upstairs.

34:11.396 --> 34:13.643
Oh, I thought we'd all be
having Jambalaya together

34:13.677 --> 34:16.545
because according to
booklover69 on your website,

34:16.580 --> 34:19.891
that's pretty much all we do
around here all day long.

34:20.152 --> 34:22.409
- Make Jambalaya?
- I think it's a euphemism.

34:22.429 --> 34:25.621
What the...
heck were you doing out there?

34:25.656 --> 34:29.062
Ugh, it was just some crazy rumor
about Regina and I.

34:29.081 --> 34:32.428
I don't know how it started,
but Lydia said to go with it.

34:32.447 --> 34:34.574
I get it. Mm-hmm.

34:34.594 --> 34:36.844
Whatever it takes to get in the club,
right?

34:36.864 --> 34:39.004
Yeah, but, honey, here's the thing.

34:39.024 --> 34:42.054
I was in the club,
and not just 'cause of some crazy rumor

34:42.074 --> 34:43.655
but because of my book.

34:43.675 --> 34:46.371
Smart, fancy people actually liked it.

34:46.391 --> 34:48.010
Of course they did, I'm not surprised.

34:48.030 --> 34:52.511
Andrea Askowitz wants
to use it in her seminar on Jane Austen.

34:52.531 --> 34:53.813
Can you believe that?

34:53.833 --> 34:55.635
Wow.

34:56.206 --> 34:57.725
You don't know who she is.

34:57.745 --> 34:59.003
I've heard of Jane Austen.

34:59.023 --> 35:00.356
(Both chuckle)

35:00.376 --> 35:03.081
I just love the feeling.
I don't know, like...

35:03.101 --> 35:05.741
I wasn't... Just the cheerleader.

35:05.761 --> 35:08.376
Honey, you've always been more
than just the cheerleader.

35:08.396 --> 35:10.481
What are you talking about?

35:10.679 --> 35:15.507
I just deeply regret the fact that I've
never seen you in your uniform.

35:15.990 --> 35:17.039
Don't get any ideas.

35:17.074 --> 35:20.702
