38:14.677 --> 38:18.077
(Sighs) I'm sorry to bug you at work.

38:18.797 --> 38:20.433
_

38:21.336 --> 38:22.564
(Sighs)

38:25.468 --> 38:28.223
It's been a crazy time,

38:29.191 --> 38:31.879
but I think I got some...

38:32.437 --> 38:34.113
clarity.

38:34.758 --> 38:36.706
I love that sign.

38:39.176 --> 38:42.097
You should go to U.S.C.

38:42.117 --> 38:45.989
And I know that it's
expensive and far away, but...

38:47.078 --> 38:49.312
You have to go...

38:51.707 --> 38:54.288
and I should come with you.

38:56.521 --> 38:57.712
_

38:58.308 --> 39:01.882
My parents have been bugging me for a plan,

39:02.415 --> 39:04.984
now I have one... yours.

39:06.002 --> 39:08.136
_

39:09.539 --> 39:13.572
I wanna be with you and I don't wanna wait.

39:13.857 --> 39:16.493
You are gonna be an amazing filmmaker.

39:16.513 --> 39:19.331
And I am gonna be a...

39:20.013 --> 39:23.773
person with no idea what she wants to do.

39:37.053 --> 39:38.182
Hey.

39:38.542 --> 39:41.381
I, um, got you your favorite.

39:46.271 --> 39:48.256
Can I talk to you for a minute?

39:49.423 --> 39:51.452
I'm kinda busy.

39:54.011 --> 39:56.433
I thought about what you said,

39:56.453 --> 39:59.808
how you felt about Angelo's
insurance settlement,

39:59.828 --> 40:03.720
and I was thinking that maybe we could

40:03.754 --> 40:07.824
use some of it to help get Melody's
new program off the ground.

40:12.098 --> 40:13.853
What program?

40:13.873 --> 40:18.382
A new deaf studies department at U.M.K.C.

40:18.402 --> 40:20.189
Through Gallaudet.

40:20.209 --> 40:22.166
I didn't know about that.

40:23.928 --> 40:27.610
And we could name it after Angelo.

40:32.337 --> 40:34.322
That could be cool.

40:34.595 --> 40:37.268
And I was thinking that, you know,

40:37.288 --> 40:40.031
maybe we could go on a
road trip this summer...

40:40.403 --> 40:42.990
Grand Canyon, Las Vegas...

40:43.176 --> 40:44.661
anywhere you want.

40:44.695 --> 40:46.663
You, me and Bay, too.

40:46.697 --> 40:48.971
Or just us two.

40:50.051 --> 40:52.012
I don't think so.

40:52.198 --> 40:53.913
Why not?

40:53.933 --> 40:56.472
Just because you give money to Melody

40:56.507 --> 40:58.864
doesn't change things between us.

40:58.884 --> 41:00.969
Angelo is still dead.

41:01.168 --> 41:03.446
How much longer is this gonna go on?

41:03.480 --> 41:06.108
Because I'm not sure I can take it.

41:07.771 --> 41:10.386
You can't take it?

41:10.421 --> 41:11.965
Daphne...

41:12.238 --> 41:14.324
I did not kill Angelo.

41:14.358 --> 41:17.460
We had an argument. People argue.

41:17.985 --> 41:20.463
I was there. I know what you said.

41:20.497 --> 41:23.078
Do you honestly think I
wanted him to drive off

41:23.098 --> 41:24.834
and have an accident?

41:24.854 --> 41:27.118
I am suffering just as much as you are.

41:27.138 --> 41:28.602
Are you?

41:28.622 --> 41:33.485
Because all I see is you working
with Chip Coto and lying to me

41:33.505 --> 41:35.180
and taking all of this money.

41:35.200 --> 41:38.342
- How did I lie to you?
- You've always lied to me...

41:38.377 --> 41:41.026
ever since you found out about the switch
and didn't tell me.

41:41.046 --> 41:44.068
Oh my God, are we back to this again?

41:44.738 --> 41:47.125
You know what? No, it's good,

41:47.145 --> 41:51.253
because finally I can see
you for who you really are.

41:52.432 --> 41:53.876
You're not my mother.

41:53.896 --> 41:57.538
You have never been my mother.

41:57.558 --> 41:59.047
(Crying)

